Body: https://i.imgur.com/tKIBKxw.jpg  TOK BOUNTY CAMPAIGN (DETAILS)  Everyone must SIGN UP on http://thetokapp.com/register.php here. If you fail to sign up, you will not be eligible to be a part of this bounty campaign. Total bounty allocated = 20,000,000 TOK Tokens (5 Million bounty per month)  Website - www.thetokapp.com  GENERAL RULES  â€¢   The Bounty TOK Team reserves the right to make changes to the conditions at any time. â€¢   Any offensive or inappropriate behaviour will lead to an immediate disqualification from the campaign. â€¢   A mandatory rule when submitting reports is the requirement to write new reports every week. You do not need to edit your old message. â€¢   Using multi-accounts, cheating and spamming are not allowed. It will result in getting all your accounts permanently banned in our system. â€¢   Rewarding of tokens depends on the approval of TOK Team. â€¢   All the posts/ tweets/ videos/ blogs/ retweets/ shares etc. should be viewable and public till the end of the bounty campaign. â€¢   The TOK team will manually be checking each entry which takes time. â€¢   The tokens will be distributed post the ICO ends, you will be updated via our official social handles. â€¢   If you have any questions please ask us directly in the thread or here: https://t.me/thetokapp  Twitter Campaign  Twitter Instructions:  â€¢   Apply to join the campaign here: Form Link â€¢   Follow our official Twitter Account - https://twitter.com/thetokapp â€¢   Your twitter account must have at least 50 real followers â€¢   Only one twitter account per person is allowed. â€¢   You must retweet and like at least 3 tweets per week from our Official twitter account â€¢   You must post at least 2 tweets per week about @thetokapp. You can only post a Max of 1 tweet per day. â€¢   You must use our hashtag (#tokfutureofcommunication) â€¢   Friends/Followers count will not be updated in the middle of the bounty. Note: We check tweets and retweets manually, so please be patient.  Rewards:  â€¢   50-1000 real followers: 50 TOK tokens/week â€¢   1001 and up: 200 TOK tokens/week  Facebook Campaign  Facebook Instructions:  â€¢   Apply to join the campaign here: Form Link â€¢   Follow and Like the official facebook page - https://www.facebook.com/thetokapp â€¢   Only one facebook account per person is allowed. â€¢   Users must have at least 100 friends â€¢   You must like and share too (both) at least 3 posts per week from our official facebook page â€¢   You must write 2 posts about TOK in a week using hashtag #tokfutureofcommunication â€¢   Friends/Followers count will not be updated in the middle of the bounty. â€¢   Posts must be in English, should be public and viewable and should be posted here every week (your post links)  Rewards:  â€¢   100-1000 real friends or real followers: 50 TOK tokens/week â€¢   1001 and above: 200 TOK tokens/week  Blog Article Campaign  Write a good article, review, or blog post about www.thetokapp.com in your words; Post that on your website or blog.  Apply to join the campaign here: Form Link  Blog/Article writing instructions:  â€¢   The article/review/blog post must have at least 250 words. â€¢   Your text must be original. Copy and stealing other contents lead to disqualification. â€¢   Low quality, badly written articles or videos will be rejected. â€¢   The audience for the posted article must be crypto related or match a use for TOK or promote the Token sale to a suitable audience. â€¢   Article/blog post must contain link to the www.thetokapp.com website OR Official Facebook OR Official Telegram group OR Official Twitter OR use hashtag         #tokfutureofcommunication â€¢   Writers should familiarize themselves with the official white papers to ensure accurate depiction of TOK App features.  Rewards:  â€¢   For Original article BIG (2000 words or more) = 500 - 1000 TOK tokens â€¢   For Original article MEDIUM (1000-2000 words) = 300 - 500 TOK tokens â€¢   For Original article SMALL (Below 1000 words) = 100 - 300 TOK tokens  BONUS: If you follow our Official Medium account - https://medium.com/@thetokapp then you will get 100 TOK tokens extra.  Video Campaign  â€¢   Describe TOK App and it's features â€¢   Video must be in good resolution â€¢   Video must be minimum 30 seconds. â€¢   You can upload them on your Youtube or facebook  etc (donâ€™t forget to share the link with us) â€¢   You will receive rewards based on the quality of an Article/Video. â€¢   Inform us about your Article/Videos here: Form Link  Rewards:  â€¢   Each video â€“ 1000 TOK tokens                                                     Telegram Campaign  Telegram Instructions:  â€¢   Apply to join the campaign here: Form Link â€¢   Telegram Join link: https://t.me/thetokapp â€¢   No spam or foul language against other members or about the project. â€¢   Discussion about the bounty is strictly prohibited. â€¢   No TOK tokens will be distributed to the person who quit the group during the ICO  Rewards:  â€¢   50 TOK tokens on joining our telegram group â€“ weekly basis â€¢   Bonus: 10 TOK Tokens, if you wear our profile pic till the end of the ICO.   Signature Campaign  Apply to join the campaign here: Form Link  Signature Instructions:  â€¢ Must make at least 7 constructive posts on Bitcoin Talk Forum per week. â€¢ Add the signature corresponding to your rank level â€¢ The Bounty Manager will update spreadsheets every week and check that the signature is still being used week after week.  Rewards:  1. Jr. Member: 50 TOK Tokens/Week 2. Member: 150 TOK Tokens/Week 3. Full Member: 300 TOK Tokens/Week 4.
